    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>For 10 minutes after drinking this astringent potion, you can’t intentionally lie and may be compelled to tell the truth. Upon drinking the potion, attempt a DC 19 Will save. You can voluntarily fail or critically fail.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The potion does not affect you.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> When you speak, you must tell the truth.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, and when someone asks you a question, you must attempt another DC 19 Will saving throw. If you fail this saving throw, you must answer the question truthfully if you are able to do so; if you succeed, you are temporarily immune to further attempts to ask the same question within the potion’s duration.</p>",
